〈胡薩維克〉是首歡快且充滿力量的電子[[民謠|民謠]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/how-eurovision-the-story-of-fire-saga-songwriting-team-paid-tribute-to-the-music-competition |title=How 'Eurovision: The Story of Fire Saga' Songwriting Team Paid Tribute to the Music Competition |date=2021-04-15 |first=Alex |last=Ritman |work=The Hollywood Reporter |accessdate=2021-05-02 |archivedate=2021-05-02 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210502184613/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/how-eurovision-the-story-of-fire-saga-songwriting-team-paid-tribute-to-the-music-competition |language=en |deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.marieclaire.com.tw/entertainment/movie/50867 |title=Netflix《歐洲歌唱大賽：火焰傳說》又被 瑞秋麥亞當斯 圈粉了！威爾法洛 笑力不減，宏偉奇觀的舒壓小品！ |date=2020-07-02 |author=派脆克 |work=美麗佳人 |language=zh |accessdate=2020-10-01 |archivedate=2020-10-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201001083757/https://www.marieclaire.com.tw/entertainment/movie/50867 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。由胖麥特老天（{{lang|en|Fat Max Gsus}}）擔任製作，{{le|阿帝‧納瑪拉松|Atli Örvarsson}}負責作曲，歌詞由胖麥特老天、[[里卡德·戈兰森|里卡德·戈兰森]]及[[沙凡·科提查|沙凡·科提查]]創作<ref name="credits" />。歌曲以[[G大調|G大調]]創作，每分鐘67拍，時長3分22秒。〈胡薩維克〉由[[威爾·法洛|威爾·法洛]]和聲、[[莫莉·桑登|莫莉·桑登]]演唱，後者演唱時的音域位在D3至E5<ref name="Music Notes">{{cite web|url=https://www.musicnotes.com/sheetmusic/mtd.asp?ppn=MN0213323 |title=Husavik (My Home Town) from Eurovision Song Contest: The Story of Fire Saga |publisher=Music Notes |accessdate=2020-10-17 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201017031147/https://www.musicnotes.com/sheetmusic/mtd.asp?ppn=MN0213323 |archivedate=2020-10-17 |language=en |deadurl=no}}</ref>。[[瑞秋·麥亞當斯|瑞秋·麥亞當斯]]雖然不是演唱者，但電影實際播放的版本融合了桑登與麥亞當斯兩人的歌聲<ref name="Will Ferrell First" />。在其中一幕，也能聽見麥亞當斯哼唱歌曲片段<ref name="vulture" />。

歌曲的開發過程不算順利，團隊為探討歌曲主題、角色故事及冰島語的演唱時機，歷經近90多個版本才完成如今的模樣<ref name="vulture" />，包含更加具有歐洲歌唱大賽特色的迪斯可舞曲版本及沒有任何管絃樂器單純只有電吉他的版本<ref name="spokesman">{{Cite web|title=After multiple versions, the composers of ‘Husavik’ hit the high note |last=Ordoña |first=Michael |url=https://www.spokesman.com/stories/2021/mar/25/after-multiple-versions-the-composers-of-husavik-h/ |date=2021-03-25 |publisher=Los Angeles Times |accessdate=2021-05-02 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210502155740/https://www.spokesman.com/stories/2021/mar/25/after-multiple-versions-the-composers-of-husavik-h/ |archivedate=2021-05-02}}</ref><ref name="Rolling Stone">{{Cite web|title=The ‘Eurovision’ Songwriters on Their Surprise Oscar Nomination |last=Grow |first=Kory |url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-features/eurovision-husavik-song-oscars-1158065/ |date=2021-04-23 |publisher=Rolling Stone |accessdate=2021-04-27 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210427221410/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-features/eurovision-husavik-song-oscars-1158065/ |archivedate=2021-04-27}}</ref>。科提查接受採訪表示〈胡薩維克〉是整部電影中最難搞的歌曲，任何改動都會讓歌曲走味<ref name="vulture">{{Cite web|title=The (Fake) Songs of Summer |last=Ebiri |first=Bilge |url=https://www.vulture.com/2020/06/eurovision-song-contest-the-story-of-fire-saga.html |date=2020-06-26 |website=[[Vulture|Vulture]] |publisher=[[Vox_Media|Vox Media]] |location=New York City |accessdate=2020-07-16 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200716012001/https://www.vulture.com/2020/06/eurovision-song-contest-the-story-of-fire-saga.html |archivedate=2020-07-16}}</ref>。作為整部電影的高潮，起初，創作團隊設計這會是個「喜劇性的時刻」，[[瑞秋·麥亞當斯|瑞秋·麥亞當斯]]飾演的席格芮會持續發出史詩般的[[C♯_(音名)|C♯]]高音。但之後團隊意識到，這部電影實際上是席格芮的故事歷程。於是將原定的喜劇結局改為更感性的結局<ref name="spokesman" />。

「家鄉」亦是歌曲的創作理念，其名稱取自兩位故事主角長大的地方，[[冰島|冰島]]同名小鎮「[[胡萨维克|胡萨维克]]」<ref name="Will Ferrell First" />。在電影準備期間，團隊曾打算在首都[[雷克雅維克|雷克雅維克]]附近拍攝以減少交通支出，但經過考量，還是決定採用胡薩維克當作故事背景。除了考量地方平衡發展，胡薩維克比其他冰島地名更容易發音<ref name="nytimes">{{Cite web |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2021/03/25/arts/music/oscars-husavik-eurovision-song-contest.html |title=A Tiny Icelandic Town Campaigns for the Oscars |last=Bjarnason |first=Egill |date=2021-03-25 |publisher=The New York Times |accessdate=2021-04-30 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210430001430/https://www.nytimes.com/2021/03/25/arts/music/oscars-husavik-eurovision-song-contest.html |archivedate=2021-04-30}}</ref>，同時它還是賞鯨聖地<ref name="Rolling Stone" />。胖麥特老天表示他把自己帶入席格芮的角色，設想如果是席格芮，會對家鄉有什麼感覺<ref name="spokesman" />。團隊中只有科提查沒有具備北歐背景，因此他透過[[谷歌翻譯|谷歌翻譯]]和[[谷歌地圖|谷歌地圖]]來瞭解小鎮<ref name="nytimes" />。

除了作為電影高潮，〈胡薩維克〉也展現劇中角色席格芮的人物弧线<ref name="variety">{{cite web |title=The Music Maestro of the ‘Eurovision’ Film, Savan Kotecha, on Keeping a Straight Face for a Climactic Power Ballad |url=https://variety.com/2021/music/news/eurovision-savan-kotecha-husavik-hometown-original-song-1234894112/ |last=Willman |first=Chris |work=Variety|date=2021-04-23 |accessdate=2021-02-20 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210220215510/https://variety.com/2021/music/news/eurovision-savan-kotecha-husavik-hometown-original-song-1234894112/ |archivedate=2021-02-20}}</ref>。歌詞「{{lang|en|Where the mountains sing through the screams of sea gulls/ Where the whales can live ’cause they’re gentle people}}（當山巒迴盪著海鷗的歌聲，鯨魚能自在生活是因為人們很溫柔）」使用了山、海鷗、鯨魚及（胡薩維克）人來歌頌故鄉<ref name="spokesman" />，並側面展現席格芮的溫柔性格<ref name="variety" />。《[[富比士|富比士]]》的苏珊娜·罗恩·凯勒（{{lang|en|Suzanne Rowan Kelleher}}）認為這是首歌頌家鄉的美麗讚歌<ref name="Forbes">{{cite web |last=Kelleher |first=Suzanne Rowan |title=This Icelandic Town Wants An Oscar And More Tourists—And It May Get Both |url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/suzannerowankelleher/2021/04/23/netflix-eurovision-song-contest-iceland-oscar/?sh=cf712e136886 |work=[[富比士|Forbes]] |date=2021-04-23 |accessdate=2021-05-02 |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210502164158/https://www.forbes.com/sites/suzannerowankelleher/2021/04/23/netflix-eurovision-song-contest-iceland-oscar/?sh=cf712e136886 |archivedate=2021-05-02 }}</ref>。[[Wiwibloggs|Wiwibloggs]]的評審苏珊娜（{{lang|en|Suzanne}}）認為歌曲與角色契合，沒能向拉斯分享和完成歌曲創作，是因為席格芮將對方看的比自己重要，而電影最後演唱〈胡薩維克〉，表示出席格芮只想要拉斯和家鄉一切的心意<ref name="wiwijury" />。

==宣傳活動==
電影發布後幾日，[[莫莉·桑登|莫莉·桑登]]首度於個人[[Instagram|Instagram]]帳戶發布歌曲表演影片<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://wiwibloggs.com/2020/07/01/molly-sanden-uploads-live-acoustic-of-husavik-to-her-my-marianne-music-instagram-account/255680/ |title=Molly Sandén uploads live acoustic of "Husavik" to her My Marianne Music Instagram account |first=William Lee |last=Adams |date=2020-07-01 |website=Wiwibloggs |accessdate=2021-01-20 |archivedate=2021-01-20 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120001043/https://wiwibloggs.com/2020/07/01/molly-sanden-uploads-live-acoustic-of-husavik-to-her-my-marianne-music-instagram-account/255680/ |language=en |deadurl=no}}</ref>。同年8月，桑登發布[[原音乐|原音乐]]版的歌曲[[音樂錄影帶|音樂錄影帶]]，影片於瑞典[[厄兰岛|厄兰岛]]拍攝，彼得·卡爾松（{{lang|en|Peter Carlsson}}）負責鋼琴伴奏<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.qx.se/noje/200314/molly-sandens-akustiska-version-av-husavik-bor-ingen-missa/ |title=Molly Sandéns akustiska version av Husavik bör ingen missa|date=23 August 2020 |first=Alfred |last=Jansson |work=QX |accessdate=2020-12-03 |archivedate=2020-12-03 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201203032849/https://www.qx.se/noje/200314/molly-sandens-akustiska-version-av-husavik-bor-ingen-missa/ |language=sv |deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://wiwibloggs.com/2020/08/18/my-marianne-shares-acoustic-video-of-husavik-filmed-on-swedens-oland-island/256826/ |title=My Marianne shares acoustic video of "Husavik" filmed on Sweden’s Öland island |first=William Lee |last=Adams |date=2020-08-18 |website=Wiwibloggs |accessdate=2020-11-29 |archivedate=2020-11-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129020301/https://wiwibloggs.com/2020/08/18/my-marianne-shares-acoustic-video-of-husavik-filmed-on-swedens-oland-island/256826/ |language=en |deadurl=no}}</ref>。在[[第93屆奧斯卡金像獎|第93屆奧斯卡金像獎]]的熱身特別節目《奧斯卡：萬眾焦點》（''{{lang|en|Oscars: Into the Spotlight}}''）中，桑登與胡萨维克當地居民一起表演歌曲<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.yahoo.com/entertainment/oscars-reveal-original-song-performers-223106805.html |title=Oscars Reveal Original Song Performers and Aftershow Plans |work=Variety |date=2021-04-16 |accessdate=2021-04-16 |archivedate=2021-04-18 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210418120838/https://www.yahoo.com/entertainment/oscars-reveal-original-song-performers-223106805.html |language=en |deadurl=no}}</ref>。

在歌曲成為當地國歌後，胡萨维克製作了一系列影片，這些影片和電影相同，都有著迷人且愚蠢的自嘲。在其中一部影片中，虛構人物胡薩維克市長奧斯卡·奧斯卡松（{{lang|en|Óskar Óskarsson}}）向鎮上人們並表示他希望歌曲能在奧斯卡之夜獲勝，並提到「很快的，我就不在是這裡唯一的奧斯卡」，隨後邀請大家一同參與在4月25日舉辦的大型奧斯卡派對<ref name="Forbes" /><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/interactive/2021/husavik-eurovision-oscars-song/ |title=Oscars song contest: The story of Husavik |first=William |last=Booth |work=Washington post |date=2021-04-23 |accessdate=2021-04-23 |archivedate=2021-04-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210423120916/https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/interactive/2021/husavik-eurovision-oscars-song/ |language=en |deadurl=no}}</ref>。真正的市長克利斯欽·马格努松（{{lang|en|Kristjan Magnusson}}）表示「這場運動的主要意義在於振奮人心，大家一起參與的樂趣才是重點，獎金則是其次」<ref name="nytimes" />。

==專業評價==
雖然電影《[[歐洲歌唱大賽：火焰傳說|歐洲歌唱大賽：火焰傳說]]》的評價毀譽參半，但觀眾和樂評卻對電影歌曲讚譽有加<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/eurovision_song_contest_the_story_of_fire_saga |title=Eurovision Song Contest: The Story of Fire Saga (2020) |website=[[爛番茄|Rotten Tomatoes]] |publisher=[[Fandango_(公司)|Fandango Media]] |accessdate=2021-04-26 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210426001832/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/eurovision_song_contest_the_story_of_fire_saga |archivedate=2021-04-26}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Eurovision Song Contest: The Story of Fire Saga Reviews |url=https://www.metacritic.com/movie/eurovision-song-contest-the-story-of-fire-saga |website=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |accessdate=2021-04-29 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210429152444/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/eurovision-song-contest-the-story-of-fire-saga |archivedate=2021-04-29}}</ref>。尤其是歐洲歌唱大賽粉絲，由於[[2020年歐洲歌唱大賽|2020年歐洲歌唱大賽]]受到[[2019冠状病毒病疫情|2019冠状病毒病疫情]]影響取消，電影的推出多少彌補比賽無法舉辦的遺憾<ref name="nytimes" /><ref name="Forbes" /><ref name="visithúsavíkur" /><ref name="visithusavik" /><ref>{{cite web |url=https://wiwibloggs.com/2020/08/10/eurovision-movie-behind-the-scenes-netflix-film-club/256684/ |title=Eurovision Song Contest: The Story of Fire Saga — Behind the scenes with Netflix Film Club |date=2020-08-10 |accessdate=2021-03-19 |first=Oliver |last=Adams |publisher=Wiwibloggs |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210319095457/https://wiwibloggs.com/2020/08/10/eurovision-movie-behind-the-scenes-netflix-film-club/256684/ |archivedate=2021-03-19}}</ref>。

[[Polygon|Polygon]]的凱倫·韓（{{lang|en|Karen Han}}）表示作為一部非音樂劇電影，歌曲的表現令人驚奇<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.polygon.com/2020/6/26/21304751/eurovision-song-contest-story-of-fire-saga-review-will-ferrell-rachel-mcadams-netflix |title=Netflix’s Eurovision Song Contest embraces Mamma Mia-esque sing-along sincerity |date=2020-06-26 |accessdate=2020-09-28 |first=Karen |last=Han |publisher=[[Polygon|Polygon]] |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200928144440/https://www.polygon.com/2020/6/26/21304751/eurovision-song-contest-story-of-fire-saga-review-will-ferrell-rachel-mcadams-netflix |archivedate=2020-09-28}}</ref>。《[[名利场_(杂志)|名利场]]》的理查·勞森（{{lang|en|Richard Lawson}}）和南[[犹他州|犹他州]]《獨立報》記者亞當·馬斯特（{{lang|en|Adam Mast}}）都認為〈胡薩維克〉就像電影《[[大娛樂家_(電影)|大娛樂家]]》的插曲〈[[大娛樂家：電影原聲帶|永不足夠]]〉<ref>{{cite web |url=https://suindependent.com/eurovision-song-contest/ |title=Movie Review: “Eurovision Song Contest: The Story of Fire Saga” |date=2020-08-10 |accessdate=2020-09-28 |first=Adam |last=Mast |publisher=SUindependent |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200928150403/https://suindependent.com/eurovision-song-contest/ |archivedate=2020-09-28}}</ref>，前者表示歌曲從英語轉變為冰島語的瞬間令人不寒而慄<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2020/06/eurovision-netflix-will-ferrell-review |title=Netflix’s Eurovision Song Contest: The Story of Fire Saga Is as Fun and Silly as It Sounds |date=2020-06-24 |accessdate=2020-06-27 |first=Richard |last=Lawson |publisher=[[名利场_(杂志)|Vanity Fair]] |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200627074058/https://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2020/06/eurovision-netflix-will-ferrell-review |archivedate=2020-06-27 }}</ref>。《[[荷里活報道|荷里活報道]]》的記者大衛·魯尼（{{lang|en|David Rooney}}）稱〈胡薩維克〉超越模仿，成為整部電影中最具音樂性的作品。壯麗的歌詞適當地緩和甜蜜負擔，為電影的結尾帶來一絲淒美<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/general-news/eurovision-song-contest-story-fire-saga-film-review-1299975/ |title=‘Eurovision Song Contest: The Story of Fire Saga’: Film Review |date=2021-04-15 |first=David |last=Rooney |work=The Hollywood Reporter |accessdate=2021-05-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210511134006/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/general-news/eurovision-song-contest-story-fire-saga-film-review-1299975/ |language=en |deadurl=no |archivedate=2021-05-11}}</ref>。來自[[Collider|Collider]]的格雷戈里·勞倫斯（{{lang|en|Gregory Lawrence}}）將歌曲列為本片第3最佳歌曲，評論到：「毫無疑問，這是首強而有力且情感豐富的歌曲。很長一段時間，我都會記得它。」，但也反應桑登的歌聲沒能和瑞秋·麥亞當斯的歌聲緊密契合，影響電影高潮帶來的震撼<ref>{{cite web |url=https://collider.com/best-eurovision-netflix-movie-songs-ranked/ |title=All the 'Eurovision' Songs Ranked, Because We Are in Double Trouble Tonight |date=2020-07-03 |accessdate=2020-12-16 |first=Gregory |last=Lawrence |publisher=[[Collider|Collider]] |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216103904/https://collider.com/best-eurovision-netflix-movie-songs-ranked/ |archivedate=2020-12-16}}</ref>。

專門報導[[歐洲歌唱大賽|歐洲歌唱大賽]]的新聞網站[[Wiwibloggs|Wiwibloggs]]根據評審團意見給予歌曲8.73/10分，評審團之一的埃斯玛（{{lang|en|Esma}}）稱莫莉·桑登的歌聲清晰且深入人心；另一名評審苏珊娜表示歌曲讓她停不下來，後半段的冰島語副歌更讓歌曲增添色彩。威廉（{{lang|en|William}}）評論〈胡薩維克〉就像是《[[风中奇缘_(电影)|风中奇缘]]》中的〈{{le|風之彩|Colors of the Wind}}〉，歌詞簡單而豐富，就算播完都還能想起它<ref name="wiwijury">{{cite web |url=https://wiwibloggs.com/2020/07/22/wiwi-jury-eurovision-movie-husavik-my-hometown/255756/ |title=Wiwi Jury: Eurovision movie – “Husavik (My Hometown)” |date=2020-07-22 |accessdate=2020-09-26 |first=Robyn |last=Gallagher |publisher=[[Wiwibloggs|Wiwibloggs]] |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926144041/https://wiwibloggs.com/2020/07/22/wiwi-jury-eurovision-movie-husavik-my-hometown/255756/ |archivedate=2020-09-26}}</ref>。《{{le|新報 (新加坡)|The New Paper|新報}}》記者喬納森·羅伯茨（Jonathan Roberts）評價：「絕對的神曲。最後一首歌（〈胡薩維克〉）絕對值得你略過整部電影，只為聽到它。」<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.tnp.sg/entertainment/movies/review-eurovision-song-contest-story-fire-saga |title=Review: Eurovision Song Contest: The Story Of Fire Saga, Latest Movies News |date=2020-07-03 |accessdate=2020-08-10 |first=Jonathan |last=Roberts |publisher=The New Paper |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200810054745/https://www.tnp.sg/entertainment/movies/review-eurovision-song-contest-story-fire-saga |archivedate=2020-08-10}}</ref>。本作導演[[大衛·多布金|大衛·多布金]]亦稱〈胡薩維克〉是整部電影當中他最引以為傲的歌曲<ref name="vulture" />。

歌曲亦獲得多個音樂和電影獎項提名；其中包括[[第93屆奧斯卡金像獎|第93屆奧斯卡金像獎]][[奥斯卡最佳原创歌曲奖|最佳原创歌曲]]提名<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2021/mar/15/the-full-list-of-2021-oscar-nominations |title=The full list of 2021 Oscar nominations |date=2021-03-15 |work=Guardian |accessdate=2021-03-15 |archive-date=2021-03-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210315191804/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2021/mar/15/the-full-list-of-2021-oscar-nominations |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[第26届评论家选择电影奖|第26届评论家选择电影奖]][[評論家選擇電影獎最佳電影原創歌曲|最佳電影原創歌曲]]提名<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://variety.com/2021/film/news/2021-critics-choice-awards-winners-list-1234922714/ |title=Critics Choice Awards 2021 Full Winners: Chloe Zhao’s ‘Nomadland’ Continues Its Reign on Awards Season |date=2021-03-07 |first=Clayton |last=Davis |work=Variety |accessdate=2021-03-07 |archive-date=2021-05-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210520213542/https://variety.com/2021/film/news/2021-critics-choice-awards-winners-list-1234922714/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>、第11屆{{le|好萊塢傳媒音樂大獎|Hollywood Music in Media Awards}}最佳劇情長片原創歌曲提名<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/awards/9517388/diane-warren-james-newton-howard-winners-2021-hollywood-music-in-media-awards/ |title=Diane Warren & James Newton Howard Among Top Winners at 2021 Hollywood Music in Media Awards |first=Paul |last=Grein |date=2021-01-27 |accessdate=2021-01-27 |work=Billboard |archive-date=2021-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128041606/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/awards/9517388/diane-warren-james-newton-howard-winners-2021-hollywood-music-in-media-awards/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並最終獲得了第2屆美國作曲家及作詞家協會獎最佳傑出原創影視歌曲<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://thescl.com/news/winners-of-the-2nd-annual-scl-awards/ |title=Winners of the 2nd Annual SCL Awards {{!}} The Society of Composers and Lyricists |work=The Society of Composers and Lyricists |language=en |accessdate=2021-03-04 |archivedate=2021-03-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210304014718/https://thescl.com/news/winners-of-the-2nd-annual-scl-awards/ |deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/soul-eurovision-song-contest-among-society-of-composers-and-lyricists-award-winners |title='Soul,' 'Eurovision Song Contest' Among Society of Composers and Lyricists Award Winners |date=2021-03-02 |first=Hilary |last=Lewis |work=[[荷里活報道|The Hollywood Reporter]] |accessdate=2021-03-08 |archivedate=2021-03-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308080837/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/soul-eurovision-song-contest-among-society-of-composers-and-lyricists-award-winners |language=en |deadurl=no}}</ref>。雖然沒能得到奥斯卡最佳原创歌曲奖，但不少媒體認為歌曲很有機會得獎，包含《[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝]]》和[[全国公共广播电台|全国公共广播电台]]<ref name="Forbes" />。前者認為歌曲應該獲獎<ref>{{cite web |title=The Music Maestro of the ‘Eurovision’ Film, Savan Kotecha, on Keeping a Straight Face for a Climactic Power Ballad |url=https://variety.com/feature/2021-oscars-best-original-song-predictions-1234784930/ |last=Davis |first=Clayton |work=Variety |date=2021-03-11 |accessdate=2021-04-14 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210414000345/https://variety.com/feature/2021-oscars-best-original-song-predictions-1234784930/ |archivedate=2021-04-14}}</ref>；後者則稱〈胡薩維克〉和其他入圍歌曲不同，它出現在電影高潮而不是片尾，不僅與電影相互配合，也為歌曲提供了絕佳的展示平台。那怕不會得獎，它也應該得到<ref>{{cite web |title=The 2021 Oscars' Best Original Song Nominees, Cruelly Ranked |url=https://www.npr.org/2021/04/21/987253460/the-2021-oscars-best-original-song-nominees-cruelly-ranked |last=Thompson |first=Stephen |work=npr |date=2021-04-21 |accessdate=2021-05-08 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210508100633/https://www.npr.org/2021/04/21/987253460/the-2021-oscars-best-original-song-nominees-cruelly-ranked |archivedate=2021-05-08}}</ref>。Vulture則認為〈胡薩維克〉獲獎不僅會是最佳原創歌曲的勝利，亦是讓大家記得本屆奧斯卡的唯一希望<ref>{{cite web |title=This Is Going to Be the Most Ridiculous Best Original Song Year Ever |url=https://www.vulture.com/2021/03/this-will-be-a-ridiculous-oscars-best-original-song-year.html |last=Reid |first=Joe |work=Vulture |date=2021-03-04 |accessdate=2021-04-20 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210420001222/https://www.vulture.com/2021/03/this-will-be-a-ridiculous-oscars-best-original-song-year.html |archivedate=2021-04-20}}</ref>。

==商業成績==
{{Multiple image|direction=vertical|image1=Will_Ferrell_2013.jpg|width1=150|footer=[[威爾·法洛|威爾·法洛]]憑藉〈胡薩維克〉首次登上《告示牌》排行榜<ref name="Will Ferrell First">{{cite news|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/business/chart-beat/9414514/eurovision-track-debuts-digital-song-sales-chart |title=Will Ferrell Scores First Charted Billboard Song With 'Eurovision' Track 'Husavik' |last=Zellner |first=Xander |date=2020-07-07 |publisher=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]] |accessdate=2020-07-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200711163824/https://www.billboard.com/articles/business/chart-beat/9414514/eurovision-track-debuts-digital-song-sales-chart |archivedate=2020-07-11 |language=en |deadurl=no}}</ref>}}

歌曲除了廣受好評，更成功登上多國音樂排行榜。發行三天內來到iTunes全球歌曲排行榜第10名<ref>{{cite web |url=https://wiwibloggs.com/2020/06/29/netflix-eurovision-song-husavik-reaches-top-10-of-worldwide-itunes-chart/255628/ |title=Netflix Eurovision song “Husavik” reaches Top 10 of Worldwide iTunes chart |date=2020-06-29 |accessdate=2021-03-03 |first=William |last=Lee Adams |publisher=[[Wiwibloggs|Wiwibloggs]] |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210303215726/https://wiwibloggs.com/2020/06/29/netflix-eurovision-song-husavik-reaches-top-10-of-worldwide-itunes-chart/255628/ |archivedate=2021-03-03}}</ref>。在美國，〈胡薩維克〉以8000次下載量登上《[[告示牌_(雜誌)|告示牌]]》數位歌曲銷售榜。是[[威爾·法洛|威爾·法洛]]首次登上《[[告示牌_(雜誌)|告示牌]]》排行榜<ref name="Will Ferrell First" />。在英國，歌曲以60名首次出現在[[英國單曲排行榜|英國單曲排行榜]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://wiwibloggs.com/2020/07/03/sweden-molly-sanden-debuts-uk-singles-chart-husavik/255841/ |title=Sweden: Molly Sandén debuts in UK singles chart with “Husavik”… on her birthday |date=2020-07-03 |accessdate=2020-09-10 |first=William |last=Lee Adams |publisher=Wiwibloggs |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200910115630/https://wiwibloggs.com/2020/07/03/sweden-molly-sanden-debuts-uk-singles-chart-husavik/255841/ |archivedate=2020-09-10}}</ref>，最高位置來到59名，並維持4周<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.officialcharts.com/search/singles/husavik/ |title=husavik {{!}} full Official Chart History |publisher=Official Charts Company |accessdate=2021-04-29 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210429174808/https://www.officialcharts.com/search/singles/husavik/ |archivedate=2021-04-29}}</ref>。蘇格蘭方面，歌曲最高位置來到[[蘇格蘭單曲和專輯榜|蘇格蘭單曲榜]]第8名<ref name="scottish" />。〈胡薩維克〉也登上其他國家榜單。包含澳大利亞、加拿大、歐洲、匈牙利、紐西蘭和瑞典，截至2021年4月，歌曲累積達到2600萬次串流次數<ref name="Forbes" />。

在冰島，歌曲空降[[冰島國家廣播公司|冰島國家廣播公司]]榜單冠軍<ref name="RÚV" />。根據Tonlist統計，〈胡薩維克〉是冰島2020年最受歡迎歌曲第18名<ref>{{cite web |url=https://plotutidindi.is/arslistar/log-2020/ |script-title=is:TÓNLISTINN – LÖG – 2020 |publisher=FHF (Record Company Association) |accessdate=2021-01-16 |language=is |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116053412/https://plotutidindi.is/arslistar/log-2020/ |archivedate=2021-01-16 }}</ref>，它在榜單上維持了14周<ref>{{cite web |url=https://plotutidindi.is/lagalistinn/ |script-title=is:Vika 40 – 25. sept. til 1. okt. 2020 |publisher=FHF (Record Company Association) |accessdate=2020-10-05 |language=is |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20201005141220/http://plotutidindi.is/lagalistinn/ |archivedate=2020-10-05 }}</ref>，最高名次到達第2名<ref name="Tonlist" />。歌曲的成功也對當地造成影響，尤其是在歌曲故事背景中的[[胡萨维克|胡萨维克]]，胡萨维克旅遊局的網站訪問人數因為歌曲的推出而急遽上升，地方商店也時常播放歌曲<ref name="visithúsavíkur">{{cite web|url=https://www.ruv.is/frett/2020/07/09/vonar-ad-eurovision-safn-a-husavik-verdi-ad-veruleika |script-title=is:Vonar að Eurovision-safn á Húsavík verði að veruleika |date=2020-07-09 |first=Nína |last=Hjördís Þorkelsdóttir |publisher=[[冰島國家廣播公司|RÚV]] |accessdate=2020-10-05 |language=is |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201005191704/https://www.ruv.is/frett/2020/07/09/vonar-ad-eurovision-safn-a-husavik-verdi-ad-veruleika |archivedate=2020-10-05}}</ref><ref name="visithusavik">{{cite web|url=https://wiwibloggs.com/2020/07/16/qa-husavik-tourism-board-says-the-eurovision-movie-was-a-blessing-for-picturesque-fishing-village/256110/ |title=Q&A: Húsavík Tourism Board says the Eurovision movie “was a blessing” for picturesque fishing village |date=2020-07-16 |accessdate=2020-10-05 |first=Robyn |last=Gallagher |publisher=Wiwibloggs |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201005192318/https://wiwibloggs.com/2020/07/16/qa-husavik-tourism-board-says-the-eurovision-movie-was-a-blessing-for-picturesque-fishing-village/256110/ |archivedate=2020-10-05}}